---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="For Advertisers - Sports Digital Network"
  description="Reach your audience where they actually spend time. National campaigns or hyperlocal targeting across Canada's premium community venues."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <h1>Reach your audience</h1>
    <p>Connect with Canadians where they actually spend their time</p>
  </section>

  <!-- National Section -->
  <section id="national" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-tag">National brands</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Scale your brand across Canada</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Premium venues. Affluent demographics. Coast-to-coast reach with one trusted partner.</p>

      <div class="hero-split">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551632811-561732d1e306?w=1200&h=800&fit=crop" alt="National campaign reach" class="hero-img">
        <div>
          <h3>One partner, national impact</h3>
          <p>Our network of 100+ premium venues gives you unparalleled access to Canada's most desirable audiences in environments where families spend quality time together.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>35M weekly impressions across major markets</li>
            <li>Consistent brand presence from Vancouver to Halifax</li>
            <li>Simplified campaign management and reporting</li>
            <li>Dynamic digital creative with instant updates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128506;</div>
          <h3>National coverage</h3>
          <p>100+ premium venues across Canada's major markets. Reach millions of engaged consumers with consistent messaging nationwide.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128106;</div>
          <h3>Premium demographics</h3>
          <p>Active, affluent families with household incomes 35% above national average. Decision-makers with real purchasing power.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128241;</div>
          <h3>Full HD digital</h3>
          <p>Showcase your products in stunning clarity. Update creative instantly. A/B test messaging across markets.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stats-bar">
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">100+</div><div class="stat-label">Premium venues</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">35M</div><div class="stat-label">Weekly impressions</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">$105K</div><div class="stat-label">Avg household income</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">350</div><div class="stat-label">Ad plays per day</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Local Section -->
  <section id="local" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-tag">Local businesses</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Your customers are already here</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Hyperlocal targeting that puts your brand in front of your neighborhood - nowhere else.</p>

      <div class="hero-split" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;">
        <div>
          <h3>Stop wasting money on wide reach</h3>
          <p>Every week, your neighbors gather at local arenas and golf courses. Families watching kids play hockey. Business owners on the back nine. Community members supporting local teams.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Only reach people in your service area</li>
            <li>90+ minute captive attention spans</li>
            <li>Flexible budgets - target just your local venue</li>
            <li>Associate with community pride and family time</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1546519638-68e109498ffc?w=1200&h=800&fit=crop" alt="Local community sports" class="hero-img">
      </div>

      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#127919;</div>
          <h3>Hyperlocal targeting</h3>
          <p>Stop paying for impressions outside your market. Our venue-based approach means you only reach actual potential customers in your community.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#9201;</div>
          <h3>Captive attention</h3>
          <p>Your audience spends 90+ minutes in our venues. They're not scrolling, not skipping, not distracted - they're present and engaged.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128176;</div>
          <h3>Affordable and flexible</h3>
          <p>No massive media buys required. Target just your neighborhood arena or expand to multiple venues as your business grows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stats-bar">
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">3.6M</div><div class="stat-label">Weekly visits</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">90min</div><div class="stat-label">Avg visit duration</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">3-5x</div><div class="stat-label">Weekly frequency</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">75%</div><div class="stat-label">Decision makers</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Ready to reach your audience?</h2>
    <p>Let's create a campaign that connects your brand with the communities that matter</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-white">Request a proposal</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
